# =============================================================================
# Fable 5 Offline Agent — .gitignore (Windows / macOS / Linux)
# https://github.com/dglogan42/Fable-Offline
#
# Ship curated markdown skills/knowledge/workflows only.
# Keep out: secrets, runtime memory/workspace, scrapes, PDFs, private .ics,
# Zoom/Google calendar credentials, Windows product keys, macOS recovery keys /
# full Installer apps / IPSW, ChromeOS Flex installer images / enrollment tokens,
# student rosters / school admin secrets, social chat/snap exports, private RSS
# URLs with tokens, stream keys, Adobe passwords, heavy creative inbox/exports,
# soak dumps, animation masters (Krita .kra, Stop Motion Studio + Cloud SM dumps,
# Blender caches/EXR), Roblox places, Inkstone/HiBridge sessions, bulk
# generated_prompts/, local web dump sandboxes (knowledge/web/_local/),
# full third_party app mirrors (inaturalist/iNaturalistAPI — ship third_party/README only),
# private GPX / OSM OAuth / iNat tokens / health diaries / patient booklets.
# Ship curated css-design-fingerprint-*.md + css-styles-media-kit.md only.
# =============================================================================

# --- Python ---
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
.Python
*.pyo
*.pyd

# Virtual environments
.venv/
venv/
env/
ENV/
.env/
.virtualenv/
.conda/

# Packaging / build
build/
dist/
*.egg-info/
.eggs/
*.egg
pip-wheel-metadata/
*.manifest
*.spec
MANIFEST

# Test / lint / type / coverage
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.coverage
.coverage.*
htmlcov/
.tox/
.nox/
.hypothesis/
.dmypy.json
pyrightconfig.json
.python-version

# Pip / install noise
pip-log.txt
pip-delete-this-directory.txt

# --- Secrets & local env ---
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
*.jks
credentials.json
secrets/
.secrets/
*.token
*.secret
*secret*
!*secret*.md.example
api_keys.*
**/id_rsa
**/id_ed25519
*.openai
*.anthropic
# Browser-exposed keys sometimes pasted into dumps — keep out of commits
*maps*api*key*
# Prefer curated privacy notes; never commit live form posts
**/private-data/

# --- IDE / editor ---
.idea/
.vscode/
*.code-workspace
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.project
.settings/
*.sublime-project
*.sublime-workspace
.fleet/

# --- OS ---
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/
*.lnk
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes

# OneDrive / sync junk (Windows)
~$*
*.tmp
*.temp

# --- Logs & scratch ---
*.log
logs/
tmp/
temp/
.cache/
*.bak
*.orig
*.old

# Jupyter
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# --- Local models & third-party agent state ---
*.gguf
*.bin
*.safetensors
models/
.openclaw/
.ollama/

# --- Fable 5 runtime (machine-local; do not commit) ---
memory/*
!memory/.gitkeep
workspace/*
!workspace/.gitkeep

# Skills / workflows / agents: ship shared seeds; ignore local sandboxes
skills/*.draft.md
skills/_local/
skills/**/__pycache__/
scripts/**/__pycache__/
agents/_local/
agents/*.local.md
workflows/_local/
workflows/*.local.json

# Soak / perf scratch (local measurements; do not commit machine-specific dumps)
*.soak.json
*.soak.log
soak-results/
perf-results/

# --- Knowledge data policy ---
# Ship curated *.md only. Ignore scrapes, binaries, private matter.
knowledge/**/*.html
knowledge/**/*-raw.html
knowledge/**/*-raw.txt
knowledge/**/scrape-*.html
knowledge/**/scrape-*.md
knowledge/**/scrape-*.txt
knowledge/**/*.pdf
knowledge/**/*.docx
knowledge/**/*.xlsx
knowledge/**/*.csv
knowledge/**/_local/
knowledge/**/matters/
knowledge/**/*confidential*
knowledge/**/*-raw*.txt
knowledge/brokers/_local/
knowledge/education/_local/
knowledge/education/lpu-raw-*.txt
# School / Google for Education / Minecraft Education — no rosters, keys, or domain secrets
# (Ship curated knowledge/education/*.md only; no student data or license dumps)
knowledge/education/*roster*
knowledge/education/*student*
!**/*student*.md.example
**/workspace-for-education*token*
**/minecraft*education*license*
**/minecraft*education*key*
**/minecraft*education*token*
**/*gamertag*roster*
**/MEE*license*
**/educommunity*cookie*
# Book Creator student books / tokens
**/bookcreator*token*
**/book-creator*student*
# Inkstone / yueimg hybrid sessions
**/inkstone*token*
**/inkstone*cookie*
**/hibridge*secret*
